{"tid":802445,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「或者有時會犯錯」艾利臣堅持繼續扭波","createTime":"2018-09-01T12:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T12:59:01.000Z","uid":44035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"770929c513a4ed80a8f155dc01538f68d50a4880","tid":802445,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:56:09.000Z","msg":"利物浦新加盟門將艾利臣比加表現不俗，協助球隊開咧3仗保持不失，但他喜歡扭波的踢法卻成為焦點，不過他表示仍會繼續此風格，因這是配合紅軍的踢法。<br />\n<br />\n紅軍周六險勝白禮頓取得3連勝，其中艾利臣比加完場前救出對方頭槌攻門成為功臣之一，但他於賽事有2次扭波亦同樣搶鏡，其中一次僅僅及時解圍帶來驚險。<br />\n<br />\n對此他說︰「我盡力協助球隊組織攻勢，假如情況需要我扭波，我便這樣做。或許有些冒險，但我們是一支從後場建立的球隊，這是利物浦的個性，或許有時會犯錯，但我們會盡力去做。」<br />\n<br />\n「希望我可幫助到球隊，這是整隊的努力，我會作出貢獻，但保持不失不主要是我的功勞。我們的鋒力很強，只要不失波便很大機會獲勝，現在球隊的氣氛很好，正前進努力爭勝。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=ipvygYGXWJ53dXn8KNPq%2BOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=65753a38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/或者有時會犯錯-艾利臣堅持繼續扭波-140242566--sow.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fsports%2F%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E6%9C%89%E6%99%82%E6%9C%83%E7%8A%AF%E9%8C%AF-%E8%89%BE%E5%88%A9%E8%87%A3%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%89%AD%E6%B3%A2-140242566--sow.html&d=ipvygYGXWJ53dXn8KNPq%2BOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=49da20fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/或者有時會犯錯-艾利臣堅持繼續扭波-140242566--sow.html</a>"},{"pid":"a1994fbea20da6237a725229f367488f015dc1d6","tid":802445,"uid":44035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"YWNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7882014d9a91654f9c12fe925d2aef27b1307f","tid":802445,"uid":44035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1994fbea20da6237a725229f367488f015dc1d6","tid":802445,"uid":44035,"like":3,